trans-unit.source: This class has been deprecated as of Visual Basic 2005.

trans-unit.source: This class provides methods for manipulating data that potentially represents a `Date` value.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe fornece métodos para manipular dados potencialmente representa um `Date` valor.

trans-unit.source: Required.
trans-unit.target: Necessário.

trans-unit.target: Retorna um valor de <see langword="Date" /> que corresponde ao objeto especificado.

trans-unit.source: The <see langword="Date" /> value that corresponds to <paramref name="Value" />.
